Session Directory  	/path/to/your/cache  	 (cache folder must set to 777)<br />
Cookie Domain 	True 	Info<br />
Force Cookie Use 	False<br />
Check SSL Session ID 	True<br />
Check User Agent 	False<br />
Check IP Address 	False<br />
Prevent Spider Sessions True<br />
Recreate Session 	False<br />
IP to Host Conversion Status 	true</p>
<p>And to look how your session store, you can open catalog/admin/includes/configuration.php search for define(’STORE_SESSIONS’, ‘db’);<br />
